    <ContentLayout>
        <div class="bg-white px-2 py-2 mb-2">
            <h2>DMCA</h2>
            <!-- wp:paragraph -->
            <p>All the content on <strong>EliteAnswers.in</strong> is either submitted to <a href="https://eliteanswers.in/">EliteAnswers.in</a> by email or is readily available in various places on the Internet and believed to be in the public domain. Content (including images and videos) posted are believed to be posted within our rights according to the U.S. Copyright Fair Use Act (Title 17, U.S. Code.)</p>
