            <!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
            <h3 class="wp-block-heading">Notification of Copyright Infringement</h3>
            <!-- /wp:heading -->

            <!-- wp:paragraph -->
            <p>EliteAnswers.in is in compliance with 17 U.S.C. § 512 and the Digital Millennium Copyright Act (“<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_Millennium_Copyright_Act" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">DMCA</a>”). It is our policy to respond to any infringement notices and take appropriate actions under the Digital Millennium Copyright Act (“DMCA”) and other applicable intellectual property laws.</p>
