            <!-- wp:paragraph -->
            <p>If your copyrighted material has been posted on EliteAnswers.in or if links to your copyrighted material are returned through any search engine and you want this material removed, you must provide a written communication that details the information listed in the following section. Please be aware that you will be liable for damages (including costs and attorneys’ fees) if you misrepresent information listed on our site that is infringing on your copyrights. We suggest that you first contact an attorney for legal assistance on this matter.</p>
            <!-- /wp:paragraph -->

            <!-- wp:paragraph -->
            <p>The following elements must be included in your copyright infringement claim:</p>
            <!-- /wp:paragraph -->

            <!-- wp:list -->
            <ul><!-- wp:list-item -->
            <li>Provide evidence of the authorized person to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed.</li>
            <!-- /wp:list-item -->

            <!-- wp:list-item -->
            <li>Provide sufficient contact information so that we may contact you. You must also include a valid email address.</li>
            <!-- /wp:list-item -->

            <!-- wp:list-item -->
            <li>You must identify in sufficient detail the copyrighted work claimed to have been infringed and including at least one search term under which the material appears in EliteAnswers.in search results.</li>
            <!-- /wp:list-item -->

            <!-- wp:list-item -->
            <li>A statement that the complaining party has a good faith belief that use of the material in the manner complained of is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law.</li>
            <!-- /wp:list-item -->

            <!-- wp:list-item -->
            <li>A statement that the information in the notification is accurate, and under penalty of perjury, that the complaining party is authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed.</li>
            <!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
            <!-- /wp:list -->

            <!-- wp:paragraph -->
            <p>Must be signed by the authorized person to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly being infringed.</p>
            <!-- /wp:paragraph -->

            <!-- wp:quote -->
            <blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
            <p><strong>Please send the infringement notice via email to <a href="mailto:eliteanswers.in@gmail.com"><em>eliteanswers.in@gmail.com</em></a></strong></p>
            <!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>
            <!-- /wp:quote -->

            <!-- wp:paragraph -->
            <p>Please allow us a day or two for an email response. Note that emailing your complaint to other parties such as our Internet Service Provider will not expedite your request and may result in a delayed response due to the complaint not properly being filed. Thanks.</p>
            <!-- /wp:paragraph -->

            <!-- wp:heading -->
            <h2 class="wp-block-heading">Contact information</h2>
            <!-- /wp:heading -->

            <!-- wp:paragraph -->
            <p>If Have Any Issue with EliteAnswers.in the we are always here to assist you on Email. The only way To contact us through email here is our email:&nbsp;eliteanswers.in@gmail.com.</p>
            <!-- /wp:paragraph -->

            <!-- wp:heading -->
